ntchdbpict000394701287.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1c s\u0129 t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh c\u1ee9u ch\u1eefa, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bruno Boban v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qua kh\u1ecfi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Slavonija Po\u017eega h\u00f4m 24/3, Bruno Boban b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u00fat b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang ng\u1ef1c \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed5 g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i m\u1ea5t tr\u00ed nh\u1edb. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hai \u0111\u1ed9i li\u1ec1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch s\u01a1 c\u1ee9u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn y t\u1ebf c\u0169ng t\u1edbi c\u1ea5p c\u1ee9u cho Bruno Boban v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1edbi b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 r\u1ea5t t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh c\u1ee9u ch\u1eefa su\u1ed1t 40 ph\u00fat, Bruno Boban \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i m\u00e3i m\u00e3i. T\u1edbi nay, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft c\u1ee7a anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Marsonia v\u00e0 Slavonija Po\u017eega c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u00e2m tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i v\u1eadt v\u1edd, \u0111\u00e1 cho c\u00f3 l\u1ec7 t\u1edbi khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u1ed5i c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 1-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 cho Marsonia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u1ec9 trong ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tin bu\u1ed3n. M\u1edbi ba tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Davide Astori ch\u01a1i cho Fiorentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eaft th\u1edf trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Udinese.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Pha b\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y \u0111i sinh m\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia </strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/26/xuatchet26032018.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"528","checkdouble":"182858"},{"date":"14:13 26/03","title":"C\u1ef1u sao Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ph\u00e1t ph\u00ec \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 35","type":"","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/26/cuu-sao-ngoai-hang-anh-phat-phi-o-tuoi-35.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;di