size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Tottenham Mido s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3 s\u1ed9 sau khi ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt n\u0103m.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuu sao Ngoai hang Anh phat phi o tuoi 35 hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ph\u00e1t ph\u00ec \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 35 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/cc-5671-1521796863.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mido (th\u1ee9 hai t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i sang) t\u0103ng c\u00e2n sau khi ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, c\u1ef1u sao Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Mido khoe \u1ea3nh anh \u0111i bi\u1ec3n v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n. C\u1ef1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ai C\u1eadp cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t ph\u00ec khi di\u1ec7n qu\u1ea7n b\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean du thuy\u1ec1n.\"Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0103n h\u1ebft m\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u00e8\", m\u1ed9t fan b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn d\u00ed d\u1ecfm. Mido cao 188 cm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMido tr\u1ea3i qua ba m\u00f9a t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n White Hart Lane sau khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 18 th\u00e1ng t\u1eeb AS Roma trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2004-2005. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1983 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1ea1i Emirates v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2007.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mido khi con khoac ao tuyen Ai Cap. Anh: NS.\" title=\"Mido khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. \u1ea2nh: NS.\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/cc2-4581-1521796863.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mido khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, anh chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Middlesbrough v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Mido tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2010-2011. Mido treo gi\u00e0y trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB Barnsley, Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Cup b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u Phi n\u0103m 2006 sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u1edf Zamalek v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mido l\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh Cup qu\u1ed1c gia Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngoisao.net<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"527","checkdouble":"182859"},{"date":"14:16 26/03","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nghi\u00eam Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa \u0111\u00f3n con trai th\u1ee9 hai","type":"","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/26/tien-ve-nghiem-xuan-tu-don-con-trai-thu-hai.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"526","checkdouble":"182861"},{"date":