i-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AS Roma c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Real Madrid trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"tin chuyen nhuong\" type=\"tin chuyen nhuong\">chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span> kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng.</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng b\u1eaft ch\u1eafc tay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady trong khung g\u1ed7, v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng Loris Karius v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho Liverpool. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u1ea5p \u1ee7 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u mang t\u00ean Alisson Becker, ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao Ederson Moraes c\u1ee7a Man City ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Brazil.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool va Real gap kho trong vu mua thu mon Alisson cua Roma hinh anh\" title=\"Liverpool v\u00e0 Real g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong v\u1ee5 mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/17/soc-liverpool-mua-thu-mon-alisson-gia-71-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"color: blue;\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a AS Roma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 26 tu\u1ed5i, Liverpool v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn g\u1eedi t\u1edbi AS Roma, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i so v\u1edbi c\u1ed9t m\u1ed9c c\u0169 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City x\u00e1c l\u1eadp cho Ederson m\u1edbi trong n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. \u1ea4y v\u1eady m\u00e0 trong \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ec9nh b\u01a1 h\u1edd h\u1eefng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u CEO Umberto Gandini nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n cu\u1ed7m Alisson ra kh\u1ecfi th\u00e0nh Rome: &ldquo;Ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh kinh t\u1ebf, t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m m\u00ecnh suy y\u1ebfu. \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n \u0111i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh th\u00ec nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, Liverpool c\u0169ng v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1eeb Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n s\u1edbm thay th\u1ebf Keylor Navas v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau n\u0103m l\u1ea7n b\u1ea3y l\u01b0\u1ee3t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi De Gea hay Courtois. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Alisson l\u1ea1i ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh, anh chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o, h\u00e3nh di\u1ec7n khi nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00f3. Vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u CLB \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n g\u00ec tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n khi \u01