\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paulo Dybala \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Juventus \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Simeone bi mat thuyet phuc Dybala toi Atletico Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Simeone b\u00ed m\u1eadt thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Dybala t\u1edbi Atletico Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/13/HLV-Simeone-bi-mat-thuyet-phuc-Dybala-toi-Atletico-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0Dybala \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Atletico Madrid quan t\u00e2m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Dybala gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-sao-khung-juventus-172-177377.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>MU quan t\u00e2m Dybala</strong></span> l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 M.U v\u00e0 Real \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i th\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd. Dybala t\u1edbi Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrang Radio Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Antoine Griezmann, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Dybala t\u1edbi Atletico Madrid l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 2 v\u1eeba qua HLV Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dybala\" title=\"Dybala\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/49FAF49A00000578-5474631-image-a-64_1520457848363.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Simeone thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Dybala t\u1edbi Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSimeone mu\u1ed1n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Atletico c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. Dybala \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a HLV Simeone, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ch\u1ea1y theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Bongda24h.vn hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh Dybala s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Juventus ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 150 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Dybala kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Juventus nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o CLB.\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Dybala \u1edf Serie A 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/256219-42720/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Dybala \u1edf Serie A 2017/18</span></div>\