op-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gianluigi Buffon l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T Italia. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt n\u00f3i v\u1edbi nhau r\u1eb1ng, Azzurri c\u1ea7n m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n b\u01b0\u1edbc ra kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng m\u01a1 h\u1ed3</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ti\u1ec1m th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-tuc-world-cup/buffon-noi-gi-khi-bi-coi-la-can-duong-the-he-tre-439-182679.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gianluigi Buffon</strong></span> c\u00f9ng d\u00e0n &ldquo;c\u1eadn v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0&rdquo; Giorgio Chiellini, Andrea Barzagli, Daniele De Rossi&hellip; sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng play-off tranh v\u00e9 v\u1edbt t\u1edbi World Cup 2018. Kh\u00f4ng ai mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c tifosi h\u1ebft th\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn t\u1ee5y c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0110TQG su\u1ed1t 1,5 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua c\u00f3 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft vi\u00ean m\u00e3n. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1eefa t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 l\u00fd tr\u00ed l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea1m tr\u00f9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u00ean l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i cho h\u1ecd. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch tri \u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y nh\u1eefng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng x\u00f4ng pha tr\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"doi hinh DT Italia Gigi va Gigio, tinh cam va ly tri hinh anh\" title=\"\u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Italia Gigi v\u00e0 Gigio, t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 l\u00fd tr\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/doi-hinh-DT-Italia-Gigi-va-Gigio,-tinh-cam-va-ly-tri-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Buffon v\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T&nbsp;Italia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng trong l\u00f2ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf m\u1ee9c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u. HLV Gian Piero Ventura \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng gh\u1ebf thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Azzurri v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1ed1ng, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n l\u00e0 Luigi Di Biagio. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia, Carlo Tavecchio d\u00f9 b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, s\u1ef1 c\u0169 k\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-italia-02h45-ngay-243-giao-huu-quoc-te-372-182700.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u0110T Italia</strong></span> c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c HLV Di Biagio thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u binh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Buffon \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n qua trong khi n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Chiellini c\u0169ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Gigi \u0111\u00e3 40 tu\u1ed5i, Giorgio c\u0169ng tr\u00f2n 34 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. Ai n\u00f3i h\u1ecd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Azzurri, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebb d\u1ed1i tr\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Italia Gigi va Gigio, tinh cam va ly tri hinh anh 2\" title=\"\u0110T Italia Gigi v\u00e0 Gigio, t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 l\u00fd tr\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/DT-Italia-Gigi-va-Gigio,-tinh-cam-va-ly-tri-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 40, Gigi \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBuffon l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft \u0110T Italia n\u0103m 1997 khi m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i. 21 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i qua, anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 176 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o, gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u0103m 2006. Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u0103m 1998 t\u1edbi 2002, Buffon l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi HLV Di Biagio tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd m\u1eebng m\u1eebng t\u1ee7i t\u1ee7i g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nhau v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch&hellip; th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng Gigi</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nBuffon x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tifosi. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m tr\u00e1ch anh khi v\u1eabn \u0111ang hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-tuc-world-cup/goc-nhin-dt-italia-da-giao-huu-can-thuc-bung-hon-439-182669.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u0110T Italia</strong></span>. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Gigi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean kh\u00e1t khao thi \u0111\u1ea5u, chinh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 x\u00f3a \u0111i nh\u1eefng \u00e1m \u1ea3nh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/buffon-noi-gi-khi-bi-coi-la-can-duong-the-he-tre-439-182679.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/14/buffon-noi-gi-khi-bi-coi-la-can-duong-the-he-tre.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/buffon-noi-gi-khi-bi-coi-la-can-duong-the-he-tre-439-182679.html\">Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb?</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau khi Buffon t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T Italia v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSu\u1ed1t h\u01a1n 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua, c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Buffon trong khung th\u00e0nh Italia l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, bi\u1ebft bao th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u1ecb nhu\u1ed1m m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u \u0111en khi \u0111\u1ee9ng sau l\u01b0ng anh. Francesco Toldo, Christian Abbiati, Angelo Peruzzi&hellip; \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u00e0 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Mattia Perin, Gianluigi Donnarumma.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPerin t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng, b\u1eaft r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc tay t\u1ea1i Serie A trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Genoa nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Italia, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Albania cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2014. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, su\u1ed1t 6 n\u0103m t\u1eeb khi l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Azurri t\u1edbi nay, ch\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i nh\u00ecn Buffon th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perin va Donnarumma tai Genoa va Milan\" title=\"Perin va Donnarumma tai Genoa va Milan\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/Perin-va-Donnarumma-tai-Genoa-va-Milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Perin v\u00e0 Donnarumma \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i CLB</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Perin kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn khi c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t Buffon qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, anh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Donnarumma \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Trong g\u1ea7n 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, Donnarumma \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin c\u1eady \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 AC Milan v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u00ean m\u1ea5t anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19. Gigio c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 c\u00e1i thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a anh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00edn mu\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Italia, xem ra ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn. Buffon \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n cho Azzurri t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebfu ni\u00ean, t\u1edbi khi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng. Gigi s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc g\u1eady? \u1ed2 kh\u00f4ng&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i 2 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Italia tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y Buffon \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 m\u1ef3 \u1ed1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh 2 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc s\u01a1 s\u1ea9y n\u01a1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng, Argentina h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon va Donnarumma\" title=\"Buffon va Donnarumma\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/Buffon-va-Donnarumma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ng\u00e0y Gigi nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Gigio c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPerin ho\u1eb7c Donnarumma v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Buffon, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. V\u00e0 th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, bao g\u1ed3m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Italia \u0111ang d\u1eebng \u1edf m\u1ee9c n\u1eeda v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 4 t\u1edbi (28/3), Italia s\u1ebd so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley c\u0169ng trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Khi \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Perin ho\u1eb7c Donnarumma s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c. Nh\u01b0ng khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Italia c\u0169ng n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay m\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y. Gigi c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, t\u1eadp trung cho ch\u1eb7ng cu\u1ed1i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea5p CLB. C\u00f2n \u0110TQG, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1edbp tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Mattia hay Gigio lo. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n c\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 phi l\u00fd tr\u00ed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 c\u1ee7a \u0110T&nbsp;Italia tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf):</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/24/iyorz_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u1ec1 Gianluigi Donnarumma \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/756514-42720/033100\">Gianluigi Donnarumma</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Italia tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-argentina-20-italia-giao-huu-quoc-te-331-182715.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 2-0 Italia (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-italia-02h45-ngay-243-giao-huu-quoc-te-372-182700.html\">Argentina 2-0 Italia: Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n Messi, Albiceleste v\u1eabn h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c binh \u0111o\u00e0n Thi\u00ean thanh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/buffon-noi-gi-khi-bi-coi-la-can-duong-the-he-tre-439-182679.html\">Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/goc-nhin-dt-italia-da-giao-huu-can-thuc-bung-hon-439-182669.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110T Italia c\u1ea7n &ldquo;th\u1ef1c b\u1ee5ng&rdquo; h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-su-world-cup/world-cup-1934-phat-xit-bong-da-va-azzuri-441-182620.html\">World Cup 1934: Ph\u00e1t x\u00edt, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 Azzurri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHo\u00e0i Dung (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"521","checkdouble":"182853"},{"date":"09:02 27/03","title":"BLV Quang Huy m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Jordan","type":"","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/29/blv-quang-huy-hlv-miura-qua-don-doc.JPG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;colo