000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, BLV V\u0169 Quang Huy \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i U23 nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Jordan.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Jordan. Do c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Asaid 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nhau 0-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n nh\u1edd l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n            <div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/jordan-vs-viet-nam-22h00-ngay-273-tran-danh-moi-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-u23-167-182908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/26/jordan-vs-viet-nam-22h00-ngay-273-tran-danh-moi-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-u23.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/jordan-vs-viet-nam-22h00-ngay-273-tran-danh-moi-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-u23-167-182908.html\">Jordan vs Vi\u1ec7t Nam (22h00 ng\u00e0y 27/3): Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23</span></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1edbi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c m\u1edbi, c\u00f9ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3...<img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BLV Quang Huy mach nuoc cho DT Viet Nam dau Jordan hinh anh\" title=\"BLV Quang Huy m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Jordan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/1/29/blv-quang-huy-hlv-miura-qua-don-doc.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>BLV Quang Huy hy v\u1ecdng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i U23 VN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, BLV V\u0169 Quang Huy cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean VTC News, BLV k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"Hy v\u1ecdng Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb trung, \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Afghanistan.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan, tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 \"lai rai\" nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi U23 Iraq c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ea7n 2 th\u00e1ng. C\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u0111ang l\u00ean sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u, tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb nh\u1eadn n\u00e0y, BLV Quang Huy c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho Asiad v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi, t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 cho t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 khung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Jordan, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e8n gi\u0169a v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Asiad s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. Khi HLV x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh mang t\u00ednh k\u1ebf th\u1eeba v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ean b\u1ed9 khung c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. M\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn h\u01a1n\" - BLV Quang Huy nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Jordan vs Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h00 ng\u00e0y 27/3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"520","checkdouble":"182917"},{"date":"09:23 27/03","title":"U19 HAGL \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U19 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf","type":"","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/u19-hagl-de-lo-nhieu-diem-yeu-tai-giai-giao-huu-u19-quoc-te.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight