>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a U19 Mito Hollyhock, HLV Graechen \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 U19 HAGL c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U19 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 ba, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 HAGL g\u1eb7p U19 Mito Hollyhock (Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n). \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a L\u00ea Minh B\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ec3 Koinuma Kanaya g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i (<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-u19-hagl-11-u19-mito-hollyhock-u19-quoc-te-2018-325-182891.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p U19 HAGL 1-1 U19 Mito Hollyhock</span></strong></span>).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Graechen danh gia diem yeu cua U19 HAGL.\" title=\"HLV Graechen \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a U19 HAGL.\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/u19-hagl-de-lo-nhieu-diem-yeu-tai-giai-giao-huu-u19-quoc-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Graechen \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a U19 HAGL.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn U19 HAGL ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau hai tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean U19 Chonburi (Th\u00e1i Lan). HLV Graechen sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a \u0111\u00e0n em C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng: &quot;Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhanh, t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng hai. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng n\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n cao nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1 ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 U19 HAGL k\u00e9m m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn. T\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n U19 Mito Hollyhock, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh. D\u00f9 th\u1eafng hay thua, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb HAGL c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, HLV Kimori Daisuke c\u1ee7a U19 Mito Hollyhock c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb may m\u1eafn, m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t c\u1ee7a U19 HAGL.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, U19 HAGL s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h30 (28/3). Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-graechen-tiet-lo-ly-do-u19-hagl-thua-nguoc-u19-seoul-291-182656.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/hlv-graechen-tiet-lo-ly-do-u19-hagl-thua-nguoc-u19-seoul.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-graechen-tiet-lo-ly-do-u19-hagl-thua-nguoc-u19-seoul-291-182656.html\">HLV Graechen ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do U19 HAGL thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U19 Seoul</span><br>\r\nHLV Graechen l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn U19 HAGL thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U19 Seoul t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U19 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"519","checkdouble":"182918"},{"date":"09:39 27/03","title":"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00e1i t\u0