u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Jordan v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m Asian Cup 2019. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF ghi l\u1ea1i:</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam vs Jordan\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Jordan\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Jordan-4.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c luy\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Jordan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam vs Jordan\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Jordan\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Jordan-5.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho '\u0111\u00e0n anh' V\u0103n L\u00e2m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam vs Jordan\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Jordan\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Jordan-93.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam chia qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng nh\u1eb1m \u00f4n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ch\u1ed1ng Jordan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam vs Jordan\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Jordan\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Jordan-92.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t d\u00f9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n cho nhau</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam vs Jordan\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Jordan\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Jordan-91.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Hai c\u1ef1u binh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i t\u1ecf ra n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong m\u1ed9t pha tranh b\u00f3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam vs Jordan\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Jordan\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Jordan-9.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (\u00e1o bib) n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c b\u1eadt cao ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam vs Jordan\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Jordan\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Jordan-8.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a \u1edf V-League, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam vs Jordan\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\