bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paris Saint-Germain \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/draxler-cong-khai-chi-trich-chien-thuat-cua-hlv-emery-184-181502.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Unai Emery t\u1ea1i PSG</strong></span>. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Les Parisiens v\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n 3 danh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd c\u1ee7a l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Emery t\u1ea1i PSG l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-dt-bi-muon-hazard-de-chi-trich-conte-184-182465.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Antonio Conte</strong></span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Chelsea. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Guardian ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e0m s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Conte \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eddi \u00f4ng l\u00ean l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG dam phan hop dong voi Conte thay Emery hinh anh\" title=\"PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Conte thay Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/25/psg-dam-phan-hop-dong-voi-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Conte</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-niu-keo-conte-o-lai-172-182413.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Antonio Conte</strong></span>, PSG c\u0169ng nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Jos\u00e9 Mourinho (Man United), Diego Simeone (Atletico Madrid) v\u00e0 Massimiliano Allegri (Juventus). Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, Mourinho c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi M.U d\u00f9 b\u1ecb Sevilla lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 CLB. C\u0169ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Simeone v\u00e0 Allegri s\u1edbm chia tay Atletico v\u00e0 Juve.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Conte \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Italia kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. \u0110T Italia sa th\u1ea3i Ventura sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eddi Conte quay l\u1ea1i song c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u00f4ng v\u1eabn th\u00edch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c cho m\u1ed9t CLB h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu t\u1edbi PSG, Conte s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c cho Chelsea: t\u1eeb 9,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/ n\u0103m l\u00ean 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/ n\u0103m. \u0110\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 l\u1edbn \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m l\u1edbn. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Emery, Conte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i gi\u00fap Les Parisiens v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. PSG chi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d v\u1edbi Neymar, Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 PSG tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/puyol-neymar-co-the-gia-nhap-real-madrid-184-182768.html\">Neymar r\u1eddi PSG ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/meunier-doa-roi-psg-de-chuyen-den-mu-184-182761.html\">Meunier d\u1ecda r\u1eddi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-tu-bo-enrique-vi-ly-do-dac-biet-197-182658.html\">PSG t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Enrique v\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kante-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-gia-nhap-psg-184-182493.html\">Kante l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n gia nh\u1eadp PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/psg-se-ban-neymar-cho-real-neu-180-182477.html\">PSG s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Neymar cho Real n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"515","checkdouble":"182792"},{"date":"02:44 26/03","title":"Sao PSG c\u00f4ng khai \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i HLV Emery","type":"","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/26/emery-meunier.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{c