h\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Paris Saint-Germain v\u1eabn m\u00e3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con h\u1ed5 gi\u1ea5y b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi ch\u1ee9 ra ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi \u00c2u, h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 tay m\u01a1 h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7c khi bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, g\u00e3 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u Ligue 1 c\u00f2n s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau hai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao PSG cong khai doi sa thai HLV Emery hinh anh\" title=\"Sao PSG c\u00f4ng khai \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i HLV Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/emery-meunier.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sao PSG c\u00f4ng khai \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i HLV Emery</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 l\u1ea5p l\u00e1nh c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh \u1edf HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 t\u00e0i nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, quy\u1ec1n uy \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u00e1p l\u1ef1c d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn b\u1edfi n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean c\u01a1m ch\u00e1o g\u00ec \u1edf Premier League, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Thomas Meunier c\u00f2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u00f4ng khai \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i HLV Emery \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tu\u1ed5i 18 n\u1eefa m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 26 r\u1ed3i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2 \u1edf CLB, cho th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i b\u1edfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 HLV v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea5y, Julian Draxler t\u1eebng c\u00f4ng khai ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a HLV Emery l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t v\u00e0 h\u00e8n nh\u00e1t d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Angel di Maria d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn nh\u01b0 Meunier nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"514","checkdouble":"182820"},{"date":"06:34 26/03","title":"PSG b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Conte","type":"","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/26/psg-bi-mat-dam-phan-voi-conte.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{co