l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal</strong></span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thomas tuchel\" title=\"thomas tuchel\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/15/HLV-Tuchel-noi-dien-sau-tran-Frankfurt-2-1-Dortmund-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal nh\u1eafm thay Wenger</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eafng tay v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Wenger b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p chia tay s\u00e2n Emirates, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-chot-xong-nguoi-thay-hlv-wenger-172-182805.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal s\u1ebd l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Thomas Tuchel</strong></span>. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 cao, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tuchel \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Tuchel</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport Buzzer, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/psg-104.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG</strong></span> l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 HLV Thomas Tuchel. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Unai Emery, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. D\u00f9 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00fap Sevilla v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League nh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft PSG l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Tuchel\" title=\"Thomas Tuchel\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/psg-tinh-cuop-thomas-tuchel-truoc-mui-arsenal.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u1ee5 Thomas Tuchel</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, PSG d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Barca c\u00f2n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Real. V\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 PSG thu v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Tuchel thay th\u1ebf nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 46 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u1ea5p \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 46 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"512","checkdouble":"182862"},{"date":"16:20 26/03","title":"Nh\u1eefng HLV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Emery d\u1eabn d\u1eaft PSG","type":"","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/26/nhung-hlv-co-the-thay-the-emery-dan-dat-psg.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}