tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG sa th\u1ea3i Unai Emery l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1eafm thay \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 46 tu\u1ed5i.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Antonio Conte</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0o v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG sa thai Unai Emery 5 muc tieu thay the hang dau hinh anh\" title=\"PSG sa th\u1ea3i Unai Emery 5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/PSG-sa-thai-Unai-Emery-5-muc-tieu-thay-the-hang-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>N\u1ebfu PSG sa th\u1ea3i Unai Emery h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 HLV Antonio Conte&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Abramovich \u0111ang t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte. Ngay c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh FA Cup v\u00e0 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a th\u00ec \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c th\u00f4i vi\u1ec7c. N\u1ebfu PSG sa th\u1ea3i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/unai-emery-etxegoien-130.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Unai Emery</strong></span>, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm Conte nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1ef1u HLV Juventus c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0110T Italia, song \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Guardian, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/psg-104.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Conte v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a, ngo\u00e0i ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Thomas Tuchel</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi b\u1ecb Dortmund sa th\u1ea3i HLV Thomas Tuchel v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea, nh\u01b0ng PSG t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Tuchel.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Thomas Tuchel\" title=\"HLV Thomas Tuchel\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/20/Diem-tin-toi-1002-MU-dai-chien-Barca-vi-sao-Roma-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Thomas Tuchel</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1edd Bild ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa Tuchel v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 44 tu\u1ed5i t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Massimiliano Allegri</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Massimiliano Allegri \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n mang v\u1ec1 cho Juventus nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. \u1ede \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft 2 trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Sau nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 50 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Massimiliano Allegri da san sang dan dat Arsenal\" title=\"Massimiliano Allegri \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/hlv-juventus-da-san-sang-thay-the-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Massimiliano Allegri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nAllegri \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. PSG ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Luis Enrique</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luis Enrique d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u HLV Barca, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 19 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a m\u00e0 v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 47 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. PSG \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Enrique, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao m\u00e0 \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Enrique\" title=\"Luis Enrique\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/20/thua-tran-hlv-luis-enrique-khong-ung-ho-juventus-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luis Enrique</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPSG c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Luis Suarez hay Marco Asensio, nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mong mu\u1ed1n. Enrique \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u00f9ng Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a 2014/15, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng gi\u00fap PSG l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Mauricio Pochettino</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u00f4ng \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn Tottenham th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1edf Premier League, \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Spurs c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. Kh\u00f4ng ti\u00eau qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o TTCN nh\u01b0ng Tottenham \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. Pochettino c\u0169ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u01b0a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Dele Alli hay Harry Kane th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mauricio Pochettino\" title=\"Mauricio Pochettino\" src=\"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/22/southampton-11-tottenham-poch-gioi-dung-nguoi-khong-phai-thay-nguoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mauricio Pochettino</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPSG mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Pochettino, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i PSG c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Tottenham \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"511","checkdouble":"182878"}]}